## ğŸ§  Overview
This project presents a one-month sales report dashboard built using Power BI. It visualizes key business metrics using two core datasets:
- `employee`: Contains employee details and identifiers.
- `sales_raw_data`: Includes transactional sales data for the reporting period.

The primary goal of this dashboard is to provide clear, interactive visualizations that help stakeholders understand sales performance, employee contributions, and product-level insights.

